"A presentation from Dr Nicholas Gruen, CEO of Lateral Economics, called 'Government as impresario: Driving innovation without money'.

In the presentation, Dr Gruen explores ideas about 'public goods privately provided' and the scope for new kinds of public private partnerships.

The presentation was co-hosted by the Department of Communications and the Department of Industry in Canberra on Tuesday 17 June 2014."

